{"tid":982990,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"離婚要分樓同贍養費好過份咩？","createTime":"2019-01-15T14:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T19:53:43.000Z","uid":22647,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"03753d4d646ef058821655aae10d16e29d3cd493","tid":982990,"uid":22647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:43:58.000Z","msg":"離婚要分樓同贍養費好過份咩？<br />\n我乜都無做錯 係你咁鬼小氣 見我同其他男人親密啲行下街唔覺意摸到手仔就話我比帽你帶  朋友唔係男就女架啦 我廿幾歲就跟你到宜家變三十到尾嘅中女 你話飛我就飛我？起碼賠層樓同贍養費比我補償翻我無價嘅青春啦 仲有我有比你屌架 男人老狗得你搵咁少錢養我都養唔起莫講話生細路 我逼不得已想泊過個好碼頭都係你一手造成架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你條八婆成撚日呻自己老公撈唔掂走去溝仔諗住騎牛搵馬 仲姣我男人收皮啦臭雞"},{"pid":"17be8604619fad1ee2e391941aa2433d60337170","tid":982990,"uid":22647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae008f5af294f374e91abab2a9503860631de120","tid":982990,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"過主啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"537091287b067abbc144e22e5f0e53a97e81e694","tid":982990,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T15:03:54.000Z","msg":"咁嘅年紀麻煩你去babycondom啦"},{"pid":"a8943b21a97844197c29eeca2ab4864d39e2a0f2","tid":982990,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"你老公係潘紹聰？"},{"pid":"96f3e3a279fec85c8261e423229ecddfe461619b","tid":982990,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T18:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b082c09714530ecdb944aea712760160add152","tid":982990,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"537091287b067abbc144e22e5f0e53a97e81e694","tid":982990,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T15:03:54.000Z","msg":"咁嘅年紀麻煩你去babycondom啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T19